<placeName ref="#place-7001215">Cairo</placeName>
, writes me a characteristic letter of 8 lines, the
<lb facs="#facs_6_r1l2" n="N002"/>
last of which runs: "We don't hear much of you, nor
<lb facs="#facs_6_l" n="N003"/>
little of
<persName ref="#person-EH078">Rosita Forbes</persName>
." Thank heaven for the first part.
<lb facs="#facs_6_r1l5" n="N004"/>
I have very despondent letters from
<persName ref="#person-EH106">Milly</persName>
- have you
<lb facs="#facs_6_r1l6" n="N005"/>
seen anything of her lately?
<anchor facs="#facs_6_r1l6"/>
